text: Kenichi Obinata (born 17 January 1968) is a Japanese rower. He competed in the men's lightweight double sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Japan Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Niigata Prefecture Category:Asian Games medalists in rowing Category:Rowers at the 1994 Asian Games Category:Asian Games gold medalists for Japan Category:Medalists at the 1994 Asian Games
